<h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #081849; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.3;">We value your feedback</h1>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #334155;">
  Hi <%= @business.owner_name.presence || @business.name %>,
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #334155;">
  We hope you're doing well!
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 28px 0; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #334155;">
  We've loved partnering with you to support and grow your business. We'd love to hear your thoughts on our partnership. Would you mind taking a minute to leave a brief review?
</p>

<!-- Call to Action Button -->
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: separate !important;">
        <tr>
          <td align="center" bgcolor="#213885" style="border-radius: 9999px;">
            <a href="<%= @link %>" target="_blank" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; color: #ECDFD2; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 9999px; border: 1px solid #213885; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0.02em;">Leave a Review &rarr;</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 28px 0 0 0; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #334155;">
  Thank you so much for your time and trust!
</p>

<p style="margin: 6px 0 0 0; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: bold; color: #081849;">
  The DevDeBizz Team
</p>
